<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">《Congress Asks Jeff Bezos — ‘Shouldn’t Twitch License Music?’》</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">《Twitch Knew About Its Music Licensing Problem Back In 2014 — This Memo Proves It》</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200803/a87c78e4595d49dfa1208f9fb5653229.jpeg" /></p>